# Backend agent scope

## Owns

- `app/`, `database/`, `routes/`, PHPUnit in `tests/`

## Campaign logic

- Matching lives in `app/Services/CampaignEngine.php`.
- Presentation / API in `app/Services/CampaignService.php`.
- Do not duplicate multiplier rules in controllers or mobile.

## Seeders

- Idempotent: `updateOrCreate` / `firstOrCreate`.
- Demo: `database/seeders/DemoCampaignsSeeder.php`, timezone on Demo Cafe.

## Verify

```bash
docker compose run --rm app php artisan test --filter=<TestName>
```

## Must not

- Bump mobile `app.json` / iOS plist (Release agent).
- Change `BUSINESS_RULES.md` without Domain gate + user approval.
